50|$|Around this time, several <b>Wraiths</b> attack Storm of the X-Men and Forge. Though {{without her}} mutant powers, Storm manages {{to hold her}} own as the Dire <b>Wraiths</b> invade Forge's building. They are {{eventually}} defeated. Meanwhile, the various Earth governments throw their support to defeating the Dire <b>Wraiths</b> with Rom employed as both {{an expert on the}} species and commander of field operations hunting down the menace. Since SHIELD's psychic personnel are essential in this effort, the Dire <b>Wraiths</b> cast deadly magic that target those personnel in particular to make their participation in the field effectively suicide. However, the psychics were determined to continue their part and Sorcerer Supreme Doctor Strange intervened on his own accord to cast a spell on them to improve their resistance to the attacks.|$|R
