5000|$|Similarly to Christianity's Satan, Kosst Amojan ("The Evil One") was a Prophet who {{was forced}} out of the Celestial Temple after a failed attempt to seize control, with the other Pah <b>Wraiths,</b> which are similar to fallen angels in Christianity. In several other incidents, the Pah <b>Wraiths</b> {{attempted}} to leave their physical prison (the [...] "Caves of Fire") and return {{to take control of the}} Celestial Temple, but none of these attempts succeeded. There continues to be a minority group on Bajor who worship the Pah <b>Wraiths</b> as the True Prophets, but they are generally shunned as outcasts and heretics.|$|R
